    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s analog peak, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential, delivering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline experience. This collector-grade specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including documented rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, with all bushings and suspension components in factory-fresh condition. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the vehicle retains all original VIN-matching panels and a pristine interior free of bolster wear or pixel degradation. A turn-key investment for the discerning driver seeking uncompromised mechanical integrity and performance.",
