    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in a condition that can only be described as showroom-fresh, this vehicle is a pristine example of automotive excellence. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, completely free from swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings, thanks to a lifetime of climate-controlled garaging and a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the leather remains supple and taut with absolutely no wear on the seat bolsters, and the factory-fresh scent persists. Every electronic component and switch functions with tactile precision, and the original protective film even remains on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule exclusively at authorized service centers. The engine bay is spotless, showing no signs of fluid seepage or heat-related wear. This sale includes the complete set of original keys, the factory window sticker, and a comprehensive binder of every service receipt since new. For the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers a rare 'time capsule' ownership experience.",
